text: Smøla is a municipality in Møre og Romsdal county, Norway. It is part of the Nordmøre region. Smøla is the 272nd most populous municipality in Norway with a population of 2,150. ==Related pages== *List of mayors in Norway that are elected until 2027 ==References== Category:Municipalities of Møre og Romsdal
title: Smøla
